OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Feasing slightly this evening and
OL,7,Fovernight mixed with clear spells in
OL,8,Fbetween. Remaining rather chilly, but
OL,9,Fthe wind and cloud preventing a frost.
OL,10,FWinds becoming lighter by dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FWinds will gradually ease
OL,13,Fthrough the day, but scattered,
OL,14,Fblustery showers continue with some
OL,15,Fwith hail. Feeling chilly in the
OL,16,Fnortherly wind with temperatures
OL,17,Fremaining below average for mid-May.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
